{"tid":2326854,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"［第1日］用行動去支援被追擊手足","createTime":"2020-12-15T15:18:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T15:55:19.000Z","uid":311309,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a18079379c36268e794d1770db60904596caa34d","tid":2326854,"uid":311309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T15:18:16.000Z","msg":"唔怕老婆打我 #59678<br />\n徐青藤 #11055<br />\n哥基屎忽！#12006<br />\nMerci_Arsene #13395<br />\nar迷 #23655<br />\n奧b #33709<br />\n新迷基特派員 #35112<br />\n新島真(鉄拳制裁) #67252<br />\nArsene永遠都存在 #97997<br />\n囉囉 #104764<br />\n新島眞 #106136<br />\n艾利絲 #165817<br />\nSaka(右翼) #260162<br />\n返六日唔撚2 #283207<br />\n醉赤壁(支持奧燒) #325684<br />\n迷上拿卡的本領 #343520<br />\n出口夏希(迷伊) #376713<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n十六位手足被利迷追殺第一日<br />\n聽日就係第二日 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知每日都有唔同嘅重要野關注<br />\n但可唔可以關注埋十六位手足<br />\n<br />\n過去咁多個鍾<br />\n利迷都係咁追殺<br />\n完全無打算放手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果我哋都唔出聲 唔關注<br />\n利迷可能都係繼續咁追殺<br />\n手足真係唔知會變成點<br />\n<br />\n呢個月真係好重要，係決定佢哋可唔可以安全<br />\n<br />\n#save16"},{"pid":"392fe9dc48a965f0e39b5982cb515c916a7105f8","tid":2326854,"uid":311309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T15:20:17.000Z","msg":"推到上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17bd9a7c891e384691387dfba3722f848a4ef953","tid":2326854,"uid":311309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T15:22:58.000Z","msg":"手足無人撐？"},{"pid":"792d1e6e44d8810af73ef897d4a17d9fa2ae19cb","tid":2326854,"uid":97997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T15:33:46.000Z","msg":"有冇人出返張卡嚟賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e66b589ba9ffe302b2c909ccb3d66197f67ad